PN,43701
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779797464
OL,3,CFamily of mum who died after BBL
OL,4,Cdemand 'Alice's law' for cosmetic
OL,5,Cindustry
OL,7,FThe family of a mother-of-five who
OL,8,Fdied after undergoing a procedure
OL,9,Fknown as Brazilian butt lift at a
OL,10,Fsalon in Gloucester has written to the
OL,11,FHealth Secretary, demanding the
OL,12,Fintroduction of "Alice's Law" to
OL,13,Fregulate the cosmetic industry.
OL,15,FAlice Webb, 33, died in September 2024
OL,16,Fafter receiving the BBL procedure from
OL,17,FJordan Parke, dubbed the "British Lip
OL,18,FKing", at a salon in Gloucester.
OL,26,@tD@QOUtD@]O]yD@ZOUzD@EO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779797464
OL,3,CFamily of mum who died after BBL
OL,4,Cdemand 'Alice's law' for cosmetic
OL,5,Cindustry
OL,7,FAlice, from Wotton-under-Edge, fell
OL,8,Fill following the cosmetic treatment.
OL,9,FShe was taken to Gloucestershire Royal
OL,10,FHospital, where she later died.
OL,12,FGloucestershire Police launched a
OL,13,Fcriminal investigation following her
OL,14,Fdeath, and a man and woman were
OL,15,Farrested on suspicion of manslaughter.
OL,16,FThe woman was later released without
OL,17,Fcharge, and an investigation was
OL,18,Fcontinuing until Jordan Parke died in
OL,19,FFebruary this year.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779797464
OL,3,CFamily of mum who died after BBL
OL,4,Cdemand 'Alice's law' for cosmetic
OL,5,Cindustry
OL,7,FNow, Ms Webb's sister, April Palmer,
OL,8,Fand her former partner Ben Kingscote
OL,9,Fhave written to Health Secretary James
OL,10,FMurray, over what they're calling a
OL,11,F"lack of regulation" within the
OL,12,Fcosmetic industry.
OL,14,FIn the letter, they wrote: "We are
OL,15,Fasking for urgent Government action to
OL,16,Fstrengthen regulation and to implement
OL,17,FAlice's Law."
OL,26,@vD@\OUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779797464
OL,3,CFamily of mum who died after BBL
OL,4,Cdemand 'Alice's law' for cosmetic
OL,5,Cindustry
OL,7,FMs Palmer said: "Alice's Law is very
OL,8,Fimportant to us as a family, as we
OL,9,Fbelieve it could prevent avoidable
OL,10,Fharm and spare other families the same
OL,11,Fheartbreak.
OL,13,F"We are specifically calling for
OL,14,Fliquid BBL procedures to be
OL,15,Frestricted, as a matter of urgency, to
OL,16,Fappropriately qualified surgeons only.
OL,17,FSince Alice's death, we have been
OL,18,Fworking with Save Face to press for
OL,19,Fthese restrictions to be introduced in
OL,20,Fher name.
OL,26,@oD@QOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779797464
OL,3,CFamily of mum who died after BBL
OL,4,Cdemand 'Alice's law' for cosmetic
OL,5,Cindustry
OL,7,F"We understand that the Department of
OL,8,FHealth and Social Care has been
OL,9,Fconsidering steps to restrict these
OL,10,Fhigh-risk procedures, but it has now
OL,11,Fbeen three years since Save Face first
OL,12,Flaunched its campaign.
OL,14,F"Had the Government acted on those
OL,15,Fwarnings when they were raised, Alice
OL,16,Fmight still be with us. Every month of
OL,17,Finaction risks further, entirely
OL,18,Fpreventable fatalities.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779797464
OL,3,CFamily of mum who died after BBL
OL,4,Cdemand 'Alice's law' for cosmetic
OL,5,Cindustry
OL,7,F"The lack of progress to date is
OL,8,Fextremely troubling, and we would
OL,9,Fwelcome a clear explanation for the
OL,10,Fdelay."
OL,12,FMr Kingscote, who is the father of Ms
OL,13,FWebb's eldest child, said he had also
OL,14,Fwritten to his MP, Simon Opher, to
OL,15,Fraise the issue.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@GO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779797464
OL,3,CFamily of mum who died after BBL
OL,4,Cdemand 'Alice's law' for cosmetic
OL,5,Cindustry
OL,7,FIn the letter to Mr Murray, Mr
OL,8,FKingscote said: "I am writing to you
OL,9,Fto urge yourself and the wider
OL,10,FGovernment to do more to get this
OL,11,Fstuff banned. The health risks of this
OL,12,Fprocedure by a non-qualified
OL,13,Fpractitioner are clear and well known
OL,14,Fto the Government.
OL,16,F"Save Face have been consistently
OL,17,Fcalling for a ban on BBL's for years,
OL,18,Fand yet here we are over 18 months
OL,19,Fafter Alice passed away and still the
OL,20,FGovernment have done nothing.
OL,26,@pD@QOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779797464
OL,3,CFamily of mum who died after BBL
OL,4,Cdemand 'Alice's law' for cosmetic
OL,5,Cindustry
OL,7,F"Unfortunately, the previous health
OL,8,Fsecretary, Mr Streeting, spent more
OL,9,Ftime going on TV talking about the
OL,10,Fdangers of this procedure and warning
OL,11,Fthe public against having it done by
OL,12,Fnon-qualified practitioners than
OL,13,Factually doing something to get it
OL,14,Fstopped.
OL,16,F"As a family, we are disgusted at the
OL,17,Flack of action from the Government,
OL,18,Fand we are hoping that you will be
OL,19,Fdifferent and finally take the action
OL,20,Fthat is necessary to prevent further
OL,21,Fdeaths.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779797464
OL,3,CFamily of mum who died after BBL
OL,4,Cdemand 'Alice's law' for cosmetic
OL,5,Cindustry
OL,7,F"All of our lives have been ripped
OL,8,Fapart. My daughter has to grow up
OL,9,Fwithout her mum; she had to go to her
OL,10,Fprom without her mum by her side,
OL,11,Freceive her GCSE results without her
OL,12,Fmum there to tell her how proud she
OL,13,Fis, and now she's learning to drive
OL,14,Fwithout her mum there to watch her
OL,15,Fdrive away for the first time.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779797464
OL,3,CFamily of mum who died after BBL
OL,4,Cdemand 'Alice's law' for cosmetic
OL,5,Cindustry
OL,7,F"Please do not allow another family to
OL,8,Fgo through this. You have the power to
OL,9,Fban this procedure imminently if you
OL,10,Fwant to; it should not have taken over
OL,11,F18 months without the Government doing
OL,12,Fanything."
OL,14,FAt a pre-inquest review earlier this
OL,15,Fweek at Gloucestershire Coroner's
OL,16,FCourt, senior coroner Katy Skerrett
OL,17,Fsaid a full inquest in front of a jury
OL,18,Fwould take place in the autumn.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779797464
OL,3,CFamily of mum who died after BBL
OL,4,Cdemand 'Alice's law' for cosmetic
OL,5,Cindustry
OL,7,FThe Government has announced proposals
OL,8,Fto make sure that BBLs and other high-
OL,9,Frisk procedures are only performed by
OL,10,Fspecified health workers.
OL,12,FA spokeswoman for the Department of
OL,13,FHealth and Social Care said: "Our
OL,14,Fsympathies are with Alice's family and
OL,15,Fall those whose lives have been
OL,16,Fdevastated by botched cosmetic
OL,17,Fprocedures.
OL,26,@uD@^O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779797464
OL,3,CFamily of mum who died after BBL
OL,4,Cdemand 'Alice's law' for cosmetic
OL,5,Cindustry
OL,7,F"This Government is taking action to
OL,8,Fcrack down on cosmetic cowboys and
OL,9,Froot out dangerous practices. Our
OL,10,Ftough new measures will ensure that
OL,11,Fonly qualified healthcare
OL,12,Fprofessionals will be able to perform
OL,13,Fthe highest-risk procedures, such as
OL,14,Fthe liquid Brazilian butt lift.
OL,16,F"For anyone considering a cosmetic
OL,17,Fprocedure, please check the provider's
OL,18,Fqualifications and insurance ` and
OL,19,Favoid treatments that appear
OL,20,Fsuspiciously cheap."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU|D@TO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
